controlit_users     ||..o{ controlit_audit_log             : acts as

' ============================================================
' NOTES
' ============================================================

note top of webhook_notifications
  Secret columns (webhook_url, bot_token, api_key,
  bearer_token, signing_secret, smtp_password) are
  stripped by MySqlNotificationConfigRepository.ScrubSecrets
  before leaving the data access boundary.
  Verified by test NotificationChannelsEndpoint_DoesNotSerializeSecrets.
end note

note bottom of controlit_users
  First-run bootstrap: if controlit_users is empty,
  BootstrapUserSeeder creates one SuperAdmin from
  CONTROLIT_BOOTSTRAP_EMAIL / CONTROLIT_BOOTSTRAP_PASSWORD.
  must_change_password = true on that seed.
  Env vars MANDATORY on first run — fail startup if missing.
end note

note bottom of controlit_refresh_tokens
  Stored only as SHA-256 hash. Plaintext value exists
  for exactly one HTTP response (the httpOnly cookie)
  then is dropped. replaced_by forms a rotation chain —
  replaying a revoked token revokes the entire chain
  (see seq-05-refresh-rotation).
end note

note bottom of controlit_audit_log
  Append-only. No DELETE endpoint.
  New audit actions in 05B:
  AUTH_LOGIN_SUCCESS, AUTH_LOGIN_FAILURE, AUTH_LOGOUT,
  AUTH_REFRESH, AUTH_PASSWORD_CHANGE,
  AUTH_PASSWORD_RESET_REQUEST, AUTH_PASSWORD_RESET_COMPLETE,
  USER_CREATE, USER_UPDATE, USER_SOFT_DELETE,
  USER_FORCE_PASSWORD_RESET.
end note

note right of events
  _event column has a reserved-word underscore prefix.
  Dapper must alias it: SELECT _event AS Event FROM events.
  P2 bug fix — do NOT rely on MatchNamesWithUnderscores.
end note

@enduml
